{"tid":356161,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個on9 分手原因","createTime":"2017-08-11T22:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T23:43:48.000Z","uid":28042,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5268fd3960bd1f06e4adb70468be67c355d9316","tid":356161,"uid":28042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T22:40:58.000Z","msg":"拋磚先<br />\n5、6年前網上識左個女仔。<br />\n咁我嗰輪煲緊頭文字D ，<br />\n嗰條女竟然話去機舖「好曳」<br />\n再去就要分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好好心機同佢解釋：日光日白去商場機舖打機，點會「曳」呀？ 同埋呢種賽車game 有軚同腳制先好玩架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌，佢竟然堅持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後我選擇做一個車手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n估唔到有人會「乖」撚到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b53e4e1cb5c90cf5d631ed6ebfe02d36821f19","tid":356161,"uid":89134,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T22:42:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/064217_7fc2bd9d28750f3bf1a56a674d76a2ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F064217_7fc2bd9d28750f3bf1a56a674d76a2ac.jpg&h=60c377f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你唔厭 我都悶啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"dd87cfe323a2ad3805a5125c98dce7f2a5e6ffa3","tid":356161,"uid":28042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T22:43:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/064217_7fc2bd9d28750f3bf1a56a674d76a2ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F064217_7fc2bd9d28750f3bf1a56a674d76a2ac.jpg&h=60c377f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你唔厭 我都悶啦</span></span></blockquote><br />\n屌 我冇上開感情台 sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c0467ac16ce1ecf933cc9d58c70051e0ab33a0","tid":356161,"uid":25379,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T22:43:42.000Z","msg":"為左打機唔要條女，on9嘅唔止佢，仲有你。"},{"pid":"e08bcb67dbaf2526c8a9000c89d2158aa9a8f7b7","tid":356161,"uid":28042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T22:45:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為左打機唔要條女，on9嘅唔止佢，仲有你。</blockquote><br />\n少少啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7366f20cbfa141536c83641ffc05c14c9cc550e","tid":356161,"uid":25379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T22:55:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>為左打機唔要條女，on9嘅唔止佢，仲有你。</blockquote><br />\n少少啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係少，係多<br />\n除非你職業係賽車手"},{"pid":"e696b2e311b7c2ad3ebaf6ce65f6c7ba589b3cbd","tid":356161,"uid":28047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T22:58:52.000Z","msg":"天氣太熱，分手"},{"pid":"b06b2bef164ec4694445d25781daa8b0d8abdbc8","tid":356161,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T23:39:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e36c43e7e0a57691006f4c0fbd0f34617613a79","tid":356161,"uid":65656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T23:41:39.000Z","msg":"太偏食 睇唔到將來 分手"},{"pid":"5c42b434d28e29dc3a8882818c4ec8589b101c05","tid":356161,"uid":24948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T23:43:48.000Z","msg":"一開始無諗清楚 分"}]}